## 性能规范

```powershell
# ❌ 低效：循环中 Write-Host
foreach ($item in $largeCollection) {
    Write-Host $item
}

# ✅ 高效：预分配集合 + Write-Output
$results = [System.Collections.ArrayList]::new($largeCollection.Count)
foreach ($item in $largeCollection) {
    $null = $results.Add($item)
}
Write-Output $results
```

